    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The difficulty formula, according to the YP, has a minimum difficulty of `131072` (`0x20000`). If you modify geth to go below that, the outcome of the difficulty formula is undefined. \r\n\r\n> Reward 3eth to solve this problem\r\n\r\nThis is an issue tracker, not a bounty-page. If you want to commission some work, look into e.g. gitcoin.  \r\n\r\nI'm closing this, since you're not actually reporting a bug in go-ethereum, but a bug in a modified version (where the bug clearly stems from the modifications made). Feel free to reopen if I misunderstood something here. ",
